<div class="thumbinner" style="width:242px;"><a href="/wiki/File:The_Earth_seen_from_Apollo_17.jpg" class="image" title="The historic Blue Marble photograph."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/The_Earth_seen_from_Apollo_17.jpg/240px-The_Earth_seen_from_Apollo_17.jpg" width="240" height="240" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:The_Earth_seen_from_Apollo_17.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
The historic <a href="/wiki/The_Blue_Marble" title="The Blue Marble">Blue Marble</a> photograph.</div>
</div>
