<p><b>Environmentalism</b> is a broad philosophy and <a href="/wiki/Social_movement" title="Social movement">social movement</a> centered on a concern for the <a href="/wiki/Conservation_movement" title="Conservation movement">conservation</a> and improvement of the <a href="/wiki/Environment_(biophysical)" title="Environment (biophysical)">environment</a>. Environmentalism is associated with the color green.</p>
